extends iframe-layout

block mainContent
    div(id='container')
        h3 Feedback
        
        div(id='feedbackSentence', style='display:none;')
            p(id='botSentence', style='display:none;') Your next partner for the upcoming round disconnected. Therefore a random selection was made in his/her place during this round and a random selection will be made next round. In the following rounds you will be paired with a real person again.
            p(id='botSentence2', style='display:none;') Your next partner disconnected. Therefore a random selection was made in his/her place during this round and a random selection will be made next round. In the following rounds you will be paired with a real person again.
            span You receive 
            //span(id='self1') 
            //|  and 
            span(id='self2') 
            |  from your own choice. 
            br
            span(id='otherSentence') Your next partner in the upcoming round chose to give 
                //span(id='other1') 
                //|  and 
                span(id='other2') 
                |  to his/her previous partner. (bottom number).
                br
                br
            span(id='otherSentenceLastRound', style="display:none;") There will be no next round, so there is no feedback about any upcoming partners.
                br
                br

        div(id='noSelection', style='display:none;')
            p You did not select any option. Therefore you receive 0 for this round and the following allocation was randomly chosen to determine your partner's payoff. If you do make any choice for more than 2 rounds the time available will be shortened.

        div(class="alert alert-danger", role="alert", id="error", style="display:none;max-width:530px;")
            strong No feedback. 
            span  There was an error during the choices stage so there is no feedback for this round. Apologies. However, the game should still work for the upcoming rounds. Please continue.
                                   
    
        div(class="panel panel-default", style="max-width:530px;")
            div(class="panel-heading") Allocation
            div(class="panel-body")
                table(style='width:100%;')
                    tr
                        td(style='height:33px;font-weight:normal;') You receive:
                        each val, index in receive
                            td(style='text-align:center;height:33px;width:30px;', class='feedbackTop', id='secondHoverTop' + index)= val
                    tr
                        td(style='border-top:1px solid black;border-bottom:1px solid black;')
                        - var i = 0;
                        while i < 9
                            td(class='feedbackMiddle', id='secondHoverMiddle' + i++) 
                    tr
                        td(style='height:33px;font-weight:normal;') Other receives:
                        each val, index in send
                            td(style='text-align:center;height:33px;width:30px;', class='feedbackBottom', id='secondHoverBottom' + index)= val

        div(id='colors', style='display:none;')
            p
                div(style='display:inline;') 
                     img(src='../pictures/yourChoice.gif')
                span  Your choice.
            p
                div(style='display:inline;') 
                     img(src='../pictures/partnersChoice.gif')
                span  Your next partner's choice. 
            p
                div(style='display:inline;')
                     img(src='../pictures/sameChoice.gif')
                span  Same choice.

        div(id='colorsNF', style='display:none;')
            p
                div(style='background:#660;display:inline;') 
                     img(src='../pictures/yourChoice.gif')
                span  Your choice. 
 

        br
        input(type='button', value='Continue', name='continue', id='continue', class='btn')
        
